BOLLOCKS="\
affirmation|affirm|affirms|aporia|aporetic|appropriates|appropriation|\
archetypical|archetype|archetypes|autonomous|autonomy|\
baudrillardian|\
commodification|\
committed|commitment|convention|conventional|conventions|cunning|cunningly|\
death of the author|\
deconstruct|deconstruction|deconstructs|deleuzian|desire|desires|\
disrupt|disrupts|\
